## Setting up OWASP Juice Shop 

-Created a folder named "ghost-protocol" on the Desktop.  

-Navigated into the folder and cloned the OWASP Juice Shop repository using: git clone https://github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop.git  

-Installed node.js and npm using: sudo apt install nodejs npm -y  

-Verified Installations:  
  node -v
  npm -v  
  
-Entered the cloned Juice Shop directory: cd juice-shop  

-Installed dependencies: npm install

-Started the Juice Shop application: npm start 

-Accessed the running instance in a browser at: http://localhost:3000  

 
